PURCHASE RECEIPT
===============
Hello <%= @reader.first_name %>,
Your purchase has been successfully processed. Here are the details:
TRANSACTION DETAILS:
- Transaction Reference: <%= @transaction_reference %>
- Purchase Date: <%= @purchase_date %>
- Content Type: <%= @content_type %>
- Total Amount: $<%= sprintf("%.2f", @amount / 100.0) %>
BOOK DETAILS:
- Title: <%= @book.title %>
- Author: <%= @author.first_name %> <%= @author.last_name %>
<% if @book.description.present? %>
  - Description: <%= truncate(@book.description, length: 200) %>
<% end %>
READING ACCESS:
You can start reading immediately using this link:
<%= ENV['FRONTEND_URL'] %>/read/<%= @book.id %>?token=<%= @reading_token %>
This reading link is valid for 4 hours. You can always access your book from your library at:
<%= ENV['FRONTEND_URL'] %>/library
Thank you for choosing our platform!
If you have any questions, please contact our support team.
ITAN E-Book Platform
Email: support@itan.app
